FcConfigGetRescanInterval(3)                                                                                                                                                  FcConfigGetRescanInterval(3)

NAME
       FcConfigGetRescanInterval - Get config rescan interval

SYNOPSIS
       #include <fontconfig/fontconfig.h>

       int FcConfigGetRescanInterval (FcConfig *config);

DESCRIPTION
       Returns  the interval between automatic checks of the configuration (in seconds) specified in config.  The configuration is checked during a call to FcFontList when this interval has passed since
       the last check.  An interval setting of zero disables automatic checks.  If config is NULL, the current configuration is used.

